Notwithstanding the restrictions on reproduction, modification, and
redistribution set forth above, reproduction, modification, and
redistribution are permitted solely for the application "cabetus"
(github.com/haya9924/cabetus) developed by the GitHub user haya9924.
This grant is LIMITED TO LETUS-RELATED CODE; CLASS- and attendance-related
code is NOT included in this grant. This grant is an individual exception
