Solely for the purpose of preparing and submitting a contribution, and
notwithstanding the prohibitions above, the following are permitted
(contribution-purpose exception):
1. Forking the public mirror (litus-source) on GitHub;
2. Modifying the source code to the extent necessary to create the
   contribution; and
3. Publishing such modifications on GitHub as a forked repository and as
   a pull request.
This exception does not permit any use other than preparing and submitting
a contribution. A forked repository may not be used as a means of
distributing or providing this software (including distribution of built
apps or APKs).
(Contributions accepted from: 2026-07-23)

